Belka Says Polish Central Bank Ready With ‘Unconventional’ Tools If Needed

-- B y   M o n i k a   R o z l a l
-- 
2011-07-26T11:45:36Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-26/belka-says-polish-central-bank-ready-with-unconventional-tools-if-needed.html
Poland ’s central bank is ready with
“unconventional” instruments to inject liquidity into the
banking system if the need arises, Governor Marek Belka of the
Warsaw-based Narodowy Bank Polski told lawmakers today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
